- NEVER disable zoom
- ALWAYS support gesture alternatives

### Responsive Design
- ALWAYS maintain accessibility across breakpoints
- ALWAYS test at different zoom levels
- ALWAYS ensure content reflows properly
- ALWAYS maintain functionality at all sizes
- NEVER hide essential content
- ALWAYS provide mobile-friendly alternatives

